## Verification Plan

### Automated/Local Tests
- Unit tests to verify Room DAO queries.
- Integration tests to check database migration scripts (if any).

### Manual Verification
- Deploying the app on a local emulator or real device.
- Testing Alarms and notifications triggering, reboot persistence, and testing deep-linking behavior by launching Notion directly on the device.
